column2: select my.*, SpecObj.*, galSpecExtra.*, galSpecIndx.*, galSpecInfo.*, galSpecLine.*, PhotoObj.* into mydb.HSC_SDSS_cat from mydb.HSC_SDSS as my JOIN SpecObj on my.id = SpecObj.bestObjID left join galSpecExtra on galSpecExtra.specObjID = SpecPhotoAll.specObjID left join galSpecIndx on galSpecIndx.specObjID = SpecPhotoAll.specObjID left join galSpecInfo on galSpecInfo.specObjID = SpecPhotoAll.specObjID left join galSpecLine on galSpecLine.specObjID = SpecPhotoAll.specObjID left join PhotoObj on PhotoObj.objID = SpecPhotoAll.bestObjID
